item.title: Millennial Jet Set
item.description: Welcome to Millennial Jet Set, the online home of the existentially stateless. About Millennial Jet Set aims to periodically serve up articles for the existentially stateless that run the gamut from serious thought-pieces to light-hearted guides, on topics including politics, arts, culture, food, among others - all imbued with sardonic humor and meant to be read half-heartedly and a good sense of fun. Trash and No Star What is existential statelessness?
